{"tid":1247652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟爬山 - 電訊戰","createTime":"2019-06-21T07:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T07:37:29.000Z","uid":234698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ac7fddb144d96f0aafc42fd427c72ddca22ffe","tid":1247652,"uid":234698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tel.directory.gov.hk/CEO_ENG.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftel.directory.gov.hk%2FCEO_ENG.html&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOeycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d197306f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tel.directory.gov.hk/CEO_ENG.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道政府電話簿係公開嘅，甚至電郵有時都會寫埋出黎；唔知佢地政庥部門點封 spam email，但如果過到 filter 一個政府人員一日收到幾千封電郵真係煩死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有電話都出左，又可以打俾佢地反映意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你見特首辦個 email 尾係 <a href=\"http://ceo.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fceo.gov.hk&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOeycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=f57e5912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ceo.gov.hk</a> ，政府又鍾意用人名做電郵，你估特首或者下面官員個電郵係乜？"}]}